*[[北蝗莺|北蝗莺]], ''Locustella ochotensis''
*[[矛斑蝗莺|矛斑蝗莺]], ''Locustella lanceolata''
*[[河蝗莺|河蝗莺]],''Locustella fluviatilis''
*[[苍眉蝗莺|苍眉蝗莺]], ''Locustella fasciolata''
*[[黑斑蝗莺|黑斑蝗莺]], ''Locustella naevia''
*[[史氏蝗莺|史氏蝗莺]], ''Locustella pleskei''
*[[斑背大尾莺|斑背大尾莺]], ''Locustella pryeri'', 从2004年<ref name=iucn>{{IUCN2008|assessors=BirdLife International| year=2008| id=148530 | title=Locustella pryeri | downloaded=2009-04-05}}</ref>
*[[四川蝗莺|四川蝗莺]], ''Locustella chengi''
